item.title: Zozoro
item.description: Zozoro is a great YBBB from the Kammerflage sire Gold Rush. His father is my favorite YBBB produced over the past few years and his mother is the combination of a vibrant YBBB named My Friend and a true F1 from two different WC that the Kammer’s acclimated recently. Very excited to work this guy into our 4th/5th generation of Ambilobe!
